# Components Guide

Key components of the application:

- [ChatMessage.tsx](mdc:src/components/ChatMessage.tsx): Main component for rendering chat messages
  - Handles markdown rendering
  - Supports code syntax highlighting
  - Manages copy functionality
  - Handles image display

- [LoadingDots.tsx](mdc:src/components/LoadingDots.tsx): Loading indicator component
  - Used during message processing and file uploads

- [Sidebar.tsx](mdc:src/components/Sidebar.tsx): Navigation sidebar component
  - Manages conversation list
  - Handles navigation between chats

- [dropdown.tsx](mdc:src/components/dropdown.tsx): Reusable dropdown component
  - Supports various anchor positions
  - Handles click outside behavior
